title: Waterpark.Tycoon-TiNYiSO
description:
-=- Proudly Presents -=-

                    Waterpark Tycoon (c) Astragon Software


Release On   : 24 may 2014              Disk Amount/Format : 1 CD ISO
Type of Game : Simulator                Media Protection   : Nothing


Jump in and take a dip in the refreshing waters of your own water park!
In Waterpark Tycoon you will be able to build the park of your dreams
with breathtaking slides, gigantic waterfalls and entertaining pool
scapes to be enjoyed by visitors big and small.

Manage all of the park s operations, build new structures and take care
of your visitor s well-being   because if they like your water park, your
finances will flourish as well!

Features:

Extensive building possibilities

Individual designing and positioning of pool scapes and waterslides

Free positioning, rotating and designing of buildings, attractions and pathways

Physically correct models

Entertaining management options

Cool story mode and relaxing sandbox mode


Burn/mount, install, play!
